Zooplankton Occupation Section data

Source: R/data.R
Zooplankton_Occupations_Sections.Rd

Zooplankton data collected along AZMP transects during individual occupations.

Zooplankton_Occupations_Sections

Format

A dataframe

section

Section name where data was collected

station

The name of the station where data was collected

latitude

The latitude at which data was collected

longitude

The longitude at which data was collected

year

The year in which data was collected

season

The season in which data was collected (Northern Hemisphere)

month

The month in which data was collected (numeric)

day

The day on which data was collected

event_id

A unique identifier for the sampling event

cruise_id

A unique identifier for the mission/cruise

sample_id

A unique identifier for the sample

depth

The depth at which data was actually collected

Details

The data can be cited as follows: Casault, B., Johnson, C., Devred, E., Head, E., Cogswell, A., and Spry, J. 2020. Optical, Chemical, and Biological Oceanographic Conditions on the Scotian Shelf and in the Eastern Gulf of Maine during 2018. DFO Can. Sci. Advis. Sec. Res. Doc. 2020/037. v + 66 p.
